dad and i just went to see pirates of the carribean.&nbsp; he&nbsp;didnt seen it yet, and he was planning on just seeing it over hbo, but this new pirates is definately is one that needs to be seen on the big screen.&nbsp; so, dad and i went out to see it.&nbsp; it was really neat seeing it again.&nbsp; and we shared a container of dibs.&nbsp; dips are little chocolate covered ice cream bites.&nbsp; remember bon bons?&nbsp; dips are just like bon bons.&nbsp; and when i was little, we would go to the movies and share bon bons.&nbsp; so, it was a nice little rememberance of the past.&nbsp; i needed it.&nbsp; i&nbsp;was sick today, so getting to remember past happier times was nice.&nbsp; there are days you just need it.&nbsp; its a healthy thing.&nbsp;&nbsp;

my first day of work went, well, good.&nbsp; it was boring, so saying it was good is kind of a misconception.&nbsp; yesterday was just all about filling out paper work, listening to the gm talk about rules, and watching these boring videos.&nbsp; there were about 20 some people there, and so i met two people.&nbsp; nice girls.&nbsp; im excited about this job.&nbsp; ill get to meet a lot of people.&nbsp; tomorrow i have to go pick up my apron, tie, and money pouch thing.&nbsp; then i start training on tuesday.&nbsp; busy busy.

other than that, its the same ol same ol.&nbsp; unpacking, grading, taking care of the animals (who are just so cute), spending time with dad, writing, reading, and stuff like that.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;

god bless!

i just got an annoynmous comment on my last entry.&nbsp; i deleted it because it was lame, and i know who it's from.&nbsp; she is doing everything possible to make leif hate me, have me hate him, make me believe he has moved on, and believe that we are not right to be together.&nbsp; ha!&nbsp; its very obvious it is her because it was annoymous.&nbsp; being threatened with harrasment charges and threatened to be sued for libel is lame.&nbsp; very lame.&nbsp; if he doesnt want to talk to me and has moved on, he will tell me himself over the phone.&nbsp; we are still engaged from the last time we talked.&nbsp; he said the only reason he left was because he wasnt sure about himself and his decisions and he wasnt confident in himself.&nbsp; he didnt leave because of us.&nbsp; and even though this certain person wants me to give up and admit defeat and believe he doesnt love me, that wont work.&nbsp; im way stronger than she thinks i am, and everything she is saying are excuses, lame threats, and lies.&nbsp; and i have proof of one of her lies, too.&nbsp; ooh, another thing she didnt know about me.&nbsp; i save things.&nbsp; ha!&nbsp; and she doesnt understand that once leif finds out that she has threatened to sue me he is going to be pissed!&nbsp; it is obvious that she is trying to scare me and does not want me in leif's life.&nbsp; well tough luck- i know different.&nbsp;&nbsp;
&lt;br&gt;
(in my opinion)
